  {panel}

(from Noel on IRC)

> serge was suggesting something along the lines (in my words) that if there was a permission associated with a scheme and/or group to edit it, that would work.

In the context of having hundreds of projects and thousands of users, and having to grant them all jira-administrator privileges..

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
